  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Accounting if there's no Brexit deal
  </h1>
</div>

  </div>
  
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph ">
    How companies can comply with UK accounting and reporting requirements after the UK leaves the EU.
  </p>

  </div>
</div>

